## Recommended Workflow
  -Start with APKTool - Decode resources and check manifest
  -Use JADX - Decompile code to understand logic
  -Run MobSF - Get automated comprehensive report
  -Use ADB - Validate findings on actual device/emulator
  -Cross-reference findings from all tools

## Example Combined Workflow
 1. APKTool - Decode resources
      apktool d app.apk -o decoded/
      cat decoded/AndroidManifest.xml | grep -E "debuggable|allowBackup"

  2. JADX - Decompile code
      jadx -d jadx_output/ app.apk
      grep -r "api_key" jadx_output/

   3. MobSF - Automated scan
        docker run -it -p 8000:8000 opensecurity/mobile-security-framework-mobsf
      # Upload APK via web interface

   4. ADB - Validate on device
        adb install app.apk
        adb logcat | grep -E "error|warning"

